title.narrative: Other Services - Contract Advisory and Assistance Service Individual Experts and Consultants. Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services - Other Contractual Services NOC

description.narrative: Combat international narcotics production and trafficking; reduce the cultivation and production of drugs; prevent the resurgence of drug production; and limit the public health effects of the drug trade through international drug control and demand reduction, prevention and treatment projects.

This award strives to combat international narcotics production and trafficking; reduce the cultivation and production of drugs; prevent the resurgence of drug production; and limit the public health effects of the drug trade trhough international drug control and demand reduction, prevention and treatment projects. More specifically, this includes Aviation Support. Covers individual experts and consultants possessing special, current knowledge, and skill which may be combined with extensive operational experience. They provide information, opinions, advice, or recommendations that enhance understanding of complex issues or improve the quality and timeliness of policy development and decision-making. Contract experts and consultants do not supervise or perform operating functions nor do they receive direct supervision. Contract experts and consultants serving on advisory committees are to be assigned to subobject code 2505.. PROG/DEV & SUPPORT - DOMESTIC. All Other Anticrime Programs.
